FT  22 FEB 94 / UK Company News: City Merchants High Yield up 38%
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
City Merchants High Yield Trust saw its net asset value per share rise by 38
per cent - from 105.7p to 146.2p - over the 12 months to end-December.
